294
00:21:39,460 --> 00:21:42,959
Dia ingin mencekik Tabib Zhang di tempat tidur dan membuatnya pingsan.

295
00:21:42,959 --> 00:21:44,820
Lalu dia menggantungnya di langit-langit.

296
00:21:44,820 --> 00:21:47,990
